lead_paragraph: Chiefs running back Jamaal Charles was placed on injured reserve Tuesday after developing some swelling in his surgically repaired right knee, leaving Kansas City perilously short of depth at the position.

headline.print_headline: AP Source: Chiefs' Charles Goes Back on IR With Knee Issue
